OL,3,CDriver on cocaine killed cyclist while
OL,4,Csearching for song on phone
OL,6,FDrug-taking driver Matthew Bates
OL,7,Fkilled a cyclist in Leicestershire by
OL,8,Framming him with his Audi, while
OL,9,Fsearching for a song on his phone.
OL,11,FBates had been using cocaine before he
OL,12,Fdrove his two young children - aged
OL,13,Ffive and eight - to football practice.
OL,14,FDuring that journey he logged onto a
OL,15,Fmusic app and hit cyclist Colin Banks,
OL,16,F64.
OL,18,FThe collision happened on the B4114
OL,19,FCoventry Road near Sharnford on
OL,20,FSunday, January 30, 2022. Bates' Audi
OL,21,FQ5 ended up on its side in a ditch.
