OL,6,FCollision investigators found he had
OL,7,Fstarted using a music app about 45
OL,8,Fseconds before the collision.
OL,10,FThey also said the bike was correctly
OL,11,Fpositioned in the road and Bates would
OL,12,Fhave been able to see Mr Banks from
OL,13,Fmore than 200 metres away on the
OL,14,Fstraight road.
OL,16,FMr Banks suffered a severe head injury
OL,17,Fand was pronounced dead at hospital.
