OL,6,FAnnalisa Banks, Colin's sister-in-law,
OL,7,Fread out a statement to the court. She
OL,8,Fsaid: "Colin's untimely and utterly
OL,9,Favoidable death has devastated his
OL,10,Ffamily and his friends. Words cannot
OL,11,Fdescribe the horror we felt on hearing
OL,12,Fabout the brutal nature of his
OL,13,Fpassing."
OL,15,FShe said Colin had "helped shape the
OL,16,Flives of hundreds of young people" in
OL,17,Fhis Scouts role. She added: "We have
OL,18,Fbeen robbed of a loving, gentle and
OL,19,Fthoughtful soul. There's not a day we
OL,20,Fdon't think about him."
