OL,6,FLeicester Crown Court also heard that
OL,7,Ffollowing his arrest, Bates, 37, of
OL,8,FBuckinghams Way, Sharnford, separated
OL,9,Ffrom his wife. His barrister, Jonathan
OL,10,FDunne, said his client had his own
OL,11,Ftiling business and was a devoted
OL,12,Ffather.
OL,14,FHe said: "He's taken his eyes off the
OL,15,Froad, the tyres have gone onto the
OL,16,Fkerb and in consequence has not been
OL,17,Flooking where he should have been
OL,18,Flooking."
