OL,6,FHe said Bates had left the family home
OL,7,Fand moved back in with his mother
OL,8,Fafter the break-up but still had
OL,9,Fregular contact with his children, now
OL,10,Faged 10 and seven.
OL,12,FHe said: "He's taken his eyes off the
OL,13,Froad, the tyres have gone onto the
OL,14,Fkerb and in consequence has not been
OL,15,Flooking where he should have been
OL,16,Flooking."
