OL,6,FAt sentencing Judge Timothy Spencer KC
OL,7,Fsaid Bates had clearly taken cocaine
OL,8,Fsome time before getting behind the
OL,9,Fwheel and should never have been
OL,10,Fdriving his children in the first
OL,11,Fplace. He jailed Bates for three years
OL,12,Fand nine months in prison, of which he
OL,13,Fwill serve at least half behind bars.
OL,15,FBates will be disqualified from
OL,16,Fdriving for five years after his
OL,17,Frelease from prison. The court said he
OL,18,Fwill also have to take an extended re-
OL,19,Ftest before he can drive again.
